Reassign to Jerome.  This is just like bugzilla 131359 which Jerome fixed on March 13, 2006.  In bugzilla 131359 the problem happened when using the new Generic Recording Framework by select File->New->Other->Test->Test From Recording.

This problem is when using the OLD recording framework (file->new->other->recording->HTTP Recording) .  It is still supposed to work, but we strongly recommend everyone use the new Generic Recording Framework instead.

Fixed by using o.e.h.test.ui.TestUIImage image factory instead of loading image
directly.
